print.io.piopublic

Enum ProductType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ProductType>
      • print.io.piopublic.ProductType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ProductType>

    public enum ProductType
extends java.lang.Enum<ProductType>
    Enumeration of all product types with their live and staging environment IDs.

    IMPORTANT: Commented values are not supported by SDK and comments should not be removed without checking.

    Product IDs must have live and staging values defined, else they must be commented.
    Author:
    Vlado
